1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,240
Otro dia...
otra vuelta

2
00:00:01,240 --> 00:00:01,840
por la ciudad.

3
00:00:01,840 --> 00:00:02,840
A ver que
encontramos.

4
00:00:02,840 --> 00:00:04,840
Hay gente
a quinientos metros

5
00:00:04,840 --> 00:00:05,560
de aqui
que le vendria

6
00:00:05,560 --> 00:00:06,640
genial esto.

7
00:00:06,640 --> 00:00:07,560
Y no tienen
ni idea

8
00:00:07,560 --> 00:00:08,240
de que existe.

9
00:00:08,240 --> 00:00:10,440
Objetos utiles,
invisibles.

10
00:00:10,440 --> 00:00:11,280
Os enseño.

11
00:00:11,280 --> 00:00:12,840
Antes de
desechar algo,

12
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:14,520
pensad.
Renovar,

13
00:00:14,520 --> 00:00:16,560
reutilizar,
compartir.

14
00:00:16,560 --> 00:00:18,120
Lo que para ti sobra,
para otro

15
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:19,080
es justo
lo que busca.

16
00:00:19,080 --> 00:00:21,240
Compartidlo
con vuestros vecinos.

17
00:00:21,240 --> 00:00:23,080
Pequeños gestos
cambian las cosas.

